{"word":"G470 - ἀνταποκρίνομαι - antapokrínomai - an-tap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee - Answer again","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνταποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antapokrínomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-tap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Answer again</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உத்தரவு சொல்லு, எதிர்த்துத் தாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to contradict in reply, to answer by contradicting, reply against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and <a href=\"#/G611 - ἀποκρίνομαι - apokrínomai - ap-ok-ree'-nom-ahee/611\">G611</a>; to <i>contradict</i> or <i>dispute:</i> - answer again, reply against.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1252/1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253/1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469/1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178/178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631/2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632/2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633/2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917/2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919/2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920/2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922/2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923/2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924/2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350/350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351/351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470/470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610/610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611/611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612/612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843/843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87/87\">G87</a>"}]}